After the prison takeover, Babanuki was tamed by Tama.', true, true, false, null, 'https://images-wixmp-ed30a86b8c4ca887773594c2.wixmp.com/f/e3326937-ab01-4757-a35a-a4d4e20a1987/decute3-682d3d42-de27-4184-b4b6-78e5dffc7269.png?token=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..NaGWzjc7BYuE_N3nNyMCX90ok2Nv2WAe-4AORvoJjls', 131, 59, null),

