('Buckingham Stussy', true, 'Miss Buckin, is a former member of both the Rocks Pirates and the illegal science institute MADS, during which she went by the name of Miss Buckingham Stussy. She is the self-proclaimed lover of the deceased Emperor Edward Newgate and the mother of Edward Weevil, a former Warlord of the Sea.
